# 2. How Many AI Agents Should You Build?

Build **7 agents** for the MVP.

These are not necessarily seven separate deployed services. They can be **seven logical agents** inside one Cloud Run backend.

## Recommended 7-Agent Design

|  # | Agent                            | Purpose                                                                                 |
| -: | -------------------------------- | --------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |
|  1 | **Orchestrator Agent**           | Controls the full flow and calls the right agent at the right step                      |
|  2 | **AI Passport Builder Agent**    | Autofills startup/mentor profile from pitch deck, website text, CV, bio, or description |
|  3 | **Evidence Extraction Agent**    | Reads documents and identifies key claims, evidence, and missing fields                 |
|  4 | **Eligibility Agent**            | Checks whether startup/mentor fits programme rules                                      |
|  5 | **Readiness & Risk Agent**       | Scores readiness and flags risks, gaps, contradictions, and missing proof               |
|  6 | **Passport & Stamp Agent**       | Recommends passport status, badges, earned stamps, and pending stamps                   |
|  7 | **Linkage Recommendation Agent** | Recommends mentors, partners, programmes, service providers, or next support path       |

This is enough to look advanced without becoming too heavy.

