# 7. MVP Agent Scope

For hackathon, do not build all advanced logic.

## Must Build

| Agent                        | Must Work? |
| ---------------------------- | ---------- |
| Orchestrator Agent           | Yes        |
| AI Passport Builder Agent    | Yes        |
| Evidence Extraction Agent    | Yes        |
| Eligibility Agent            | Yes        |
| Readiness & Risk Agent       | Yes        |
| Passport & Stamp Agent       | Yes        |
| Linkage Recommendation Agent | Yes        |

## Can Be Simplified

| Area                | Simplification                       |
| ------------------- | ------------------------------------ |
| Document parsing    | Use pasted text or simple PDF upload |
| Website extraction  | Let user paste website text          |
| LinkedIn import     | Let mentor paste profile text        |
| Voice input         | Skip for MVP                         |
| QR verification     | Mock public verification page        |
| PDF passport export | Optional                             |
| Real email sending  | Skip or simulate                     |
| Complex scoring     | Use prompt-based scoring             |

